#### App Module
**File**: `/back-end/src/app.module.ts`
- Configures TypeORM with MySQL database connection
- Uses ConfigService for environment variables (DB_HOST, DB_PORT, DB_USERNAME, DB_PASSWORD, DB_DATABASE)
